  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: d96a28b1a864e1c4486c2b946f8a6f5a, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "So it\u2019s not like we can have a robo-phobic company president,
    even if only by association. I kinda wanna make some real bad sound, if you get
    my drift. Robo-phobes should just all be shot, right? Like if you support organic,
    you get the bullet. Should I bring this to the press?"
